# day 7

- making a form and validating with function

```
$( "button" ).on( "click", validate );

function validate(){
  
  var thing = $( "input" ).val();

    console.log(thing);

    if (isNaN(thing)) {
      $( "div" ).append("chea error nice try");
      $( "body" ).prepend("stop");
    }  else {
      console.log("valid"); 
      $( "div" ).append("nice job you chose " + thing);

      
    }
}
```

