# Complex Arrays
```
// complex functions pg 95
function size(w, h, d) {
  var sqf = w * h;
  var vol = w * h * d;
  var chooseYourAdventure = [sqf, vol]
  return chooseYourAdventure;
}

var sixFloorSqf = size(3,3)[0]  //[0]to get sqf 6f
var sixFloorVol = size(3,3,553)[1]  //[1]to get vol 6f
```
